data.description: This generational property is finally ready to swap owners! With the  MOST unique workshop you've ever seen, stick-built, fully insulated, fully  heated & cooled with another master bedroom suite inside! There is a full  kitchen, living room, and plenty of extra space for truly whatever you  desire. This property has entertained hundreds of people at a time, and  the pasture is waiting for more horses! Just a short drive into Athens,  this 10 acres of unique peace and tranquility will check all of the boxes  for your family. Set an appointment to view today!
